id: pm-github-epdt
title: Export defaults to dry-run; real writes need --apply AND --repo
description: "Safety: pm github export prints a would-create/would-update plan by default. Real POST/PATCH to GitHub only when --apply (or --no-dry-run) AND --repo <owner/repo> are BOTH present and a token resolves. Replaces the prior --push-only path (kept --push as alias of --apply for back-compat)."
